{"title_page": "Nagoya", "text_new": "{{short description|Largest city in the Ch\u016bbu region of Japan}}\n{{Other use}}\n{{distinguish|Nogoy\u00e1}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| name                    = {{raise|0.2em|Nagoya}}\n| native_name             = {{lower|0.1em|{{nobold|{{lang|ja|\u540d\u53e4\u5c4b\u5e02}}}}}}\n| official_name           = City of Nagoya<ref>[http://www.city.nagoya.jp/global/en/ Nagoya's official English Name] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100202011555/http://www.city.nagoya.jp/global/en/ |date=2010-02-02 }}</ref>\n| settlement_type         = [[Cities designated by government ordinance of Japan|Designated city]]\n<!-- images, nickname, motto --->\n| image_skyline           = {{Photomontage\n| photo1a = Nagoya Night View.jpg|px200{{!}}\n| photo2a = Legoland japan.jpg{{!}}\n| photo2b = Higashiyamashokubutu7.JPG{{!}}\n| photo3a = 180405 Tenshu and Honmaru Goten of Nagoya castle 2.jpg{{!}}\n| photo3b = Tvtower1.jpg{{!}}\n| photo4a = Meiko Central Bridge 20170704A.jpg{{!}}\n| photo4b = Aquarium + Giant wheel + Fuji Icebreaker - view from the lighthouse - Nagoya Port - Japan (15676490678).jpg{{!}}\n| spacing = 2\n| color_border              = white\n| color                     = white\n| size = 300\n| position = center \n| space   = 2\n| foot_montage = \n}}\n| imagesize               =\n| image_alt               =\n| image_caption           = From top left:Down Town of Nagoya, [[Higashiyama Zoo and Botanical Gardens]], [[Nagoya TV Tower]], [[Nagoya Port]], Triton Bridge, [[Nagoya Castle]], [[Legoland Japan Resort]]\n| image_flag              = Flag of Nagoya, Aichi.svg\n| flag_alt                =\n| image_seal              =\n| seal_alt                =\n| image_shield            =\n| shield_alt              =\n| image_blank_emblem      = Emblem of Nagoya, Aichi.svg\n| nickname                =\n| motto                   =\n<!-- maps and coordinates ---